I am writing to express my strong interest in the BS Junior Java Software Engineer position on the BEES platform. With extensive hands-on experience in Java, Spring Boot, and microservices, combined with a proactive, collaborative mindset, I am confident I can contribute meaningfully to your cross-functional team from day one.

